ja:"デンヘルデル帝国では「闇のような漆黒の髪と血のように赤い瞳の怪物が全てを破壊するだろう」という言い伝えがありました。しかしある日皇帝の寵愛を受けた踊り子が言い伝え通りの子どもを産み落とすと事態は一変します。 呪われた子だと信じられているその子を皇帝は何度も殺そうとしますが、何をやっても効果はありませんでした。そして「レイタン(呪われた子)」と名付けられます。 レイタンは幼い頃から虐げられ痛めつけられながら息を殺して生きてきました。 しかし23歳の時母の死をきっかけに復讐が始まります。 皇室の人間である証の金髪碧眼の者を容赦なく皆殺しにするレイタン。 その対象は同じように皇宮で育ちながらも母の身分の低さから冷遇され実の母親からも虐待を受けて育ってきたセッツも例外ではありませんでした。 助けてほしいと必死で訴えますが聞き入れられず容赦なく首を斬り落とされます。 その瞬間あまりの理不尽さに恨みが募るセッツ。 一体自分が何をしたというのか…皇宮では兄妹から虐められ母からも虐待を受けて誰からも愛されず辛く寂しい時間を過ごしてきた自分がレイタンの虐めをなす術もなく傍観していたことがそれほど罪深いことなのかと…目覚めるとそこは5年前でした。初めは夢かと疑いますが段々これが現実だと悟るセッツ。今度こそ兄であるレイタンに取り入って生き残って見せると決意しますが…

広島に住む平凡な高校生・黒川は、

ある日の帰り道、黒川の目の前に血で汚れたYシャツを着た白木が現れる。

放っておくことができず「一緒に逃げよう」と彼を連れ出す黒川。
行き先も決めず飛び乗った電車、二人きりの逃避行は

ただのクラスメイトだった黒川と白木は次第に心を通わせていくが、
その終わりはあっけなく訪れる。

つかの間の逃避行から数年後、横浜の中学校で教師として働く黒川は、

column5: description:{"ja":"コスメ会社に勤めていた前世を持つエリーは、ひょんなことから王太子妃候補である公爵令嬢・アリアンヌの侍女に任命される。ところが対面したアリアンヌの姿に驚愕！ 肌は荒れ、喪服にヴェールをすっぽり被った引きこもり令嬢だったのだ！ どうやら原因は、父親の再婚で突然できた継母と義妹にある様子。エリーは前世の知識を活かして、まずはお嬢様の肌を綺麗にするために動き出すけど――？"}

column17: as she reaches for an answer."

description:{"en":"Pa Si happened to encounter Qing’s pheromone
column6: which smelled similar to a catnip. This encounter made Pa Si
column8: greedy for Qing’s pheromone. With his attention and attraction only focused on Qing
column9: he tries to stimulate Qing’s pheromones by making him angry. The road to mutual understanding is long and it would take the two of them a long time with inevitable mistakes. Pa Si only regarded Qing as a Catnip
column10: but he also wondered…what if Qing was the one destined to him?"}

column7: description:{"en":"1. Yajuu Kanojo  \nNaruse likes beautiful things
column8: so he wants to go out with Misuzu
column9:
but the moment he does she turns into a beast?!  
  
2. Ookami Kareshi  
Continuation of Yajuu Kanojo. This time it's Riku who becomes a beast in Misuzu's eyes. How will she cope?  
  
3. Onnaji Mesen (Eye to Eye)  
Hana used to be a lot taller than Souta. Now that they're in high school
column10: everything has changed. Now he's the taller one with a hoard of fans as he is the ace of basketball. Everyday
column11:
the distance between the two seems to drift further apart…  
  
4. Bianca  
The androgynous second year basketball ace
column12: Aida Leona has been confessed by the kouhai Mori Kenta. Thinking he was gay
column14: she turned him down instantly. Leo had a crush on a beautiful girl she encountered at middle school
column15: and thus the only person she ever was interested in. But Kenta is persistent
column16: and Leo may have found a connection from Kenta
column17:
to finally find her mysterious crush…  
  
5. Chimudondon  
Satoru moves to Okinawa and is bored out of his mind because there's nothing to do. Can he find something that gets his heart pumping?  
  
6. Boku no Kirai na Akuma (Evil Resident)  
Maa-kun is plagued by a demon that only he can see! How can he get rid of it?"}

column11: a genius student was tired of the boring world. While he was thinking of recreating the world
column13: he may be able to do that. After a year of testing with his classmates
their encounter turns out to be more than just a coincidence
column14: as their closeness slowly turns into something more intimate.   \n  \nLily Love… is a story between two very different people
column16: learn to trust each other in order to nurture and protect the love they share regardless of position
column18: or gender.   \n  \nIf finding true love already seems next to impossible
column19: how much harder will it be to keep it?"}

column6: description:{"en":"At the end of the yearly winter
column7: when the Tetsugome Zorainu (or \"Celestial Dog\") is to chose its bride
column8: all the girls are hidden within their houses
column9: afraid that they might be chosen.   \n  \nYuzu
column10: a young boy living in a household of all girls
column11: is made the black sheep of the family and sent out to do chores. A chance encounter by the lake with Shuro

column8: is a cute and naïve young wife. However
column9: Shino has a secret... In fact
column10: Shino is a former kunoichi! Shino asks (?) Mika
column12: to help her with her dark work if she doesn't want to be exposed to her husband
column14: who seeks mediocreness. A slapstick SEXY action unfolded by two kuichi!!"}

column9: description:{"en":"Second Lieutenant Mononobe Yuu has been sent to Midgard
column10: to attend the all-girl's school where his sister Mitsuki is the student council president. The school is specifically for people who have \"D\" powers
column11: who are needed to fight dragons
column12: and both Mitsuki and Yuu fit the criteria. On his arrival
column13: he meets and befriends another classmate named Iris Freya
column14: who is having difficulties with her \"D\"-related schoolwork. They will do their best to succeed in this dangerous world."}

column7: description:{"en":"By the time the universe was formed
column8:
it was connected with a record which covered everything.  
  
And it was called “Acacia Records”  
  
“Acacia Records” was regarded as a symbol of wisdom of the whole universe.  
  
Even Gods and Demons also yearned to reach the root of the universe."}

column10: description:{"en":"From Serenus Dreamers:  \nAoi - a girl who lives in a household of seven. Her current status? Poor. Masafumi
column12: lives in a mansion with a household of mostly servants and his grandparents. His current status? Rich. When Masafumi decides to throw away 40 cents which Aoi could have used
column13: she's enraged at his action of discarding the valuable amount
column14: and vows to never forgive him! But
column15: what happens when fate brings Aoi to the Prince's door
column17:

小説のキャラクターに憑依してしまった主人公リテーラ・ミルト。

悲惨なエンディングを回避するため

今生こそハッピーエンドを迎えるために

***
